Text: c'mon ladies - pls seed a while - i'd love this mix..
Any chance this can be seeded, i'm desperate to see if it's the mix i had on cassette tape, now sadly deceased :(

I too had this on cassette and after listening to one of his White Noise sessions just yesterday I was wondering if I'd ever find it again (just emigrated back to the UK after 7 years overseas).  Alas, no need too!  What a wicked mix, and with John Peel too - can't wait to play it again!!!   Anyone in the UK wanting to hear him or similar should be at Atomic Jam this weekend.... www.atomic-jam.com :P

THANKS HEAPS for this brilliant upload!!!

Oh!   It's not the Peel mix - but stll, AWESOME!!!  A lot of the same tracks as the Peel session.

Anyone with the Peel session from '95?
I should update - the John Peel session is, well, not.  It was ALWAYS the Essential Mix - I was confused.  WHAT a mix this is, LOVE it.
